name: Visible Thoughts: 008
description:
008 of the Visible Thoughts series.

What is freedom? That's a pretty loaded question yet everyone will answer it in their own way, shaped by their unique life experiences. Some would say freedom is political, that your liberty is determined by the policies and laws passed by power-biased government officials. Some would say freedom is to live in the wilderness where you're no longer governed by such people. Some would say freedom is what you can take from your day-to-day -- small moments where you linger a little longer and savour it. I'm not sure what freedom means to me, but now that I've travelled for months, learned to overcome my fears, moved out on my own (and did all this with my best friend and partner), I think I'm starting to get an idea.
